game_description: Demo of Jungle Passthrough - create a jungle in your home with a sample of the plants and animals from the full game "Jungle Passthrough" that can be moved to create your own customer jungle, some plants on full random spawn in demo - optional handtracking - bonus passthrough samples to interact with from other games in the lobby Compare to the full game with 70+ Plants and jungle objects, 60+ Animals, 5+ bonus pieces of furniture with various premade levels and spawnable items
